sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor V as Visitante
  participant S as Site (index.html)
  participant F as Formspree API

  V->>S: Preenche form (nome, email, mensagem)
  V->>S: Click "Enviar"
  S->>S: validate (client-side)
  alt valid
    S->>F: POST /form-id (JSON)
    F-->>S: 200 OK
    S->>V: "Mensagem enviada!"
  else invalid
    S->>V: "Preencha todos os campos"
  end
